org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface LevelMonitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItemFeatureEntry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LevelMonitorImpl

    public interface LevelMonitor
extends ItemFeatureEntry
    A representation of the model object 'Level Monitor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Preset
    • Cap
    • Severity
    • Lower Ok
    • Included Ok
    • Prefix
    • Demote Prefix
    • Suppress Events
    • Require Ack
    • Monitor Type

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getLevelMonitor()
